Check out my newest PvP Map
Gold Rush | http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QZ7yPrFN3iY

2 Games Of Cube Control | http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E9DVrak-r8c

Cube Control is a PvP bed wars map by Xisuma. Follow either of these links to download the map.

Map Download @ Planet Minecraft
http://www.planetminecraft.com/project/cube-control-pvp-bed-wars/

Map Download @ Minecraft Forums
http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1499717-cube-control-pvp-bed-wars-12w38b/

*Warning* This map requires Snapshot 12w38b http://www.mojang.com/2012/09/minecraft-snapshot-12w38b/

This map is inspired by cluster chunk, a great pvp map of the same genre. I'd like to say thank you to three_two for the inspiration and a big thanks to sciguyryan who spent a lot of time helping me put this map together.

Cluster Chunk
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HBpWO1LUlIo
